OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782652704
OL,3,CSteve Clarke steps down after Scotland
OL,4,Cknocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FScotland's manager Steve Clarke has
OL,7,Fstepped down after his side was
OL,8,Fknocked out of the World Cup on
OL,9,FSaturday.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Football Association
OL,12,Fdescribed Clarke as their "most
OL,13,Fsuccessful National Team Head Coach"
OL,14,Fas they announced his resignation
OL,15,Ffollowing seven years in charge.
OL,17,FScotland's departure from the 2026
OL,18,FWorld Cup was confirmed on Saturday
OL,19,Fnight after Croatia beat Ghana 2-1 in
OL,20,FPhiladelphia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
