OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782652704
OL,3,CSteve Clarke steps down after Scotland
OL,4,Cknocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FClarke's side mustered three points
OL,7,Ffrom nine in Group C, with a minus-
OL,8,Fthree goal difference, but as
OL,9,Fexpected, it was not enough to secure
OL,10,Fa place among the eight best third-
OL,11,Fplaced teams who move through to the
OL,12,Flast-32 of the competition.
OL,14,FAfter losing 3-0 to Brazil in their
OL,15,Ffinal group game, the Scots needed a
OL,16,Fseries of results to go in their
OL,17,Ffavour, most of which did not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782652704
OL,3,CSteve Clarke steps down after Scotland
OL,4,Cknocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FBy Saturday, Scotland required
OL,7,Ffavourable outcomes in three group
OL,8,Ffixtures, the first of which was in
OL,9,FGroup L where Ghana had to beat
OL,10,FCroatia by at least three goals.
OL,12,FHad Ghana done Scotland a favour, a
OL,13,Fdraw between DR Congo and Uzbekistan
OL,14,Fwould have suited Scotland in Group K,
OL,15,For an Uzbekistan win by no more than
OL,16,Fthree goals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
