FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782652704
OL,3,CSteve Clarke steps down after Scotland
OL,4,Cknocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FIf it came down to Group J, Scotland
OL,7,Fwould have needed Austria to beat
OL,8,FAlgeria by two goals, or Algeria to
OL,9,Fwin by four goals, but almost
OL,10,Finevitably, it was all academic and
OL,11,Fthe Scots began packing their bags.
OL,13,FClarke's squad went through their
OL,14,Fpaces at MLS side Charlotte FC's
OL,15,Ftraining base on Saturday lunchtime
OL,16,Fbefore returning to their city centre
OL,17,Fhotel in the afternoon to await their
OL,18,Ffate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
