OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782652704
OL,3,CSteve Clarke steps down after Scotland
OL,4,Cknocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FScotland, who have never qualified for
OL,7,Fthe knockout stages of a major
OL,8,Fcompetition, began their first World
OL,9,FCup campaign in 28 years with a hard-
OL,10,Ffought 1-0 win over Caribbean minnows
OL,11,FHaiti in the Boston stadium, with
OL,12,Fmidfielder John McGinn scoring the
OL,13,Fdecisive goal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
