PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782652704
OL,3,CSteve Clarke steps down after Scotland
OL,4,Cknocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FThe Scots, backed in the USA by tens
OL,7,Fof thousands of Tartan Army, then
OL,8,Fsuffered a 1-0 defeat by AFCON
OL,9,Fchampions Morocco at the same venue
OL,10,Fafter losing a goal in 70 seconds
OL,11,Fbefore a sobering and, in parts, self-
OL,12,Finflicted loss to five-times winners
OL,13,Fof the competition, Brazil, in Miami.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
