OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782652704
OL,3,CSteve Clarke steps down after Scotland
OL,4,Cknocked out of World Cup
OL,6,FSince taking over as boss in 2019,
OL,7,FClarke has guided Scotland to three
OL,8,Fout of four major finals, but like
OL,9,FEuro 2020 and Euro 2024, the Scots
OL,10,Fhave faltered at the group stage,
OL,11,Fwhich has elicited stinging criticism
OL,12,Ffrom frustrated supporters who have
OL,13,Fwatched just four goals in nine games
OL,14,Fin those finals, with the concession
OL,15,Fof 16.
